Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:20.32,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}一直相信著自己內心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.68,0:22:23.03,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}即使 身處的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:28.02,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:34.84,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}只要有著想要保護之物…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.73,0:22:41.72,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}你為誰而伸出了右手？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:47.53,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}釋放出了 數以千計的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:50.10,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}這動作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.04,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}這眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:58.00,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}都讓我心頭一緊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:04.38,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}對你不離不棄




Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園都市第三位的超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光閃閃妹 御坂美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是我失憶前的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上她那突然出現在眼前 一個模子出來的的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這兩位耍得團團轉的我 上条当麻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時 我還沒有察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個「妹妹」的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底意味著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:56.12,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,400)\pos(100,44)\fs15\fscy94}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:56.12,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,400)\pos(60,60)}{\fscx92}#11{\fscx98\b0} 妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這逃跑的姿態算什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股還扭得這麼歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在誘惑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.44,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(470,440)}<Accelerator>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺 一方通行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反射...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在可惜 這跟老子的本質不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.97,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,440)}<Vector>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是「矢量變換」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動量 熱量 電量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的矢量 光是碰到我的皮膚就可能進行變更
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然默認是設定為「反射」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下來是雙淘汰賽的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正觸摸著血液的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓它逆流的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的身體會變成怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對的人就獎勵...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安樂的永眠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 那傢伙跑去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御...坂...？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪一下啊 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話 希望你能陪我們一起到案發現場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 屍體原本...應該在這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年 這裡什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的...真的有人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本預定是等作業完成以後就回到你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂先行道歉道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以將你認作御坂妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 到頭來這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 直到剛才那一刻 我還以為你死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 看你好像完好無缺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂的確已經死亡了哦 御坂報告道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你 到底抱著什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:50.76,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(453,440)}<Pass>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一 我要跟你對暗號 御坂言出必行道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZXC741ASD852QWE963 御坂試驗你道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:06.93,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(223,440)}<Decode>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你不能解讀剛才的暗號 你好像不是實驗的相關人員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂確認道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這睡袋裡面裝的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:16.56,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,440)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妹妹哦 御坂回答道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為棄這黑貓而去的事情而道歉 御坂說道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 將動物捲入無用的戰鬥當中 會讓我很不舒服 御坂辯解道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來因為本實驗 讓你多擔心了呢 御坂道歉道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實你用不著擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也知道是你去報警的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在場的御坂 都是御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到今天 一直跟你接觸的御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.14,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,440)}<Series Number>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是標本編號10032
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是這個御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「御坂」應用操縱電力的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓相互間的腦電波相連
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是讓其他的御坂共享10032號的記憶罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂補充說明道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:41.72,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,440)}<Level 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:41.72,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(610,440)}<Original>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園都市中僅存的七位超能力者 御坂美琴姐姐大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:48.85,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(604,440)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為量產軍用模型而造的體細胞克隆體—妹妹 御坂回答道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是實驗罷了 御坂回答道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於詳細情況乃機密事項 不能向你說明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這並不帶有刑事案件性質 御坂辯明道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對將你捲入到本實驗當中 我深感抱歉 御坂低頭道歉道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭 小貓就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗？軍用？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底為什麼要在這裡亂逛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 那傢伙知道這回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於小姬神是吃閑飯的 首先要這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 為了老師我 趕快烤肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 我先說個在學園都市發生的恐怖故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師我可不會被七個不可思議之流就嚇哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉焦的部分所含的成分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是致癌物質
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種現實存在的恐怖話題 可不是夏季的風景詩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是計劃削減我的食慾 然後自己獨佔這些肉嗎 小姬神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然估計是傳閱板報之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬神 請你懇切地應對一下人家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師我 就趁這空隙 自顧自烤肉～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後自顧自吃了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我肚子餓...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少...至少讓這孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只讓史芬克斯吃點也好...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪当麻這麼久都不回來 我還以為要餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 不就是多了一兩個人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個「豪華絢爛烤肉套裝」 是不會讓人因量不足而留下遺憾的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～有肉吃 有肉吃 有肉吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站 第七學區 常盤臺初中學生宿舍前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,208號室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到那傢伙 我要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問她那個能隨隨便便就去殺一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人討厭的實驗的內容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 呃 是御坂嗎 我是上条...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...上条先生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我弄錯了房間的號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟姐姐大人是同房
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這聲音好像在哪裡聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 您的聲音我好像聽過...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是昨天跟姐姐大人幽會的那位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找姐姐大人有何貴幹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 沒啥大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大事還特地跑過來 太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她不在的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找姐姐大人有事的話 我推薦你進裡面等著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,208號室 就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進 門沒上鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會在那以後跟姐姐大人行差踏錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒有 肯定沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:17:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 看你也不像過來說這種輕佻的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等姐姐大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請坐在那張床上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 這樣實在有點不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒有得到她本人的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是我的床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...這邊就是御坂的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在別人床上幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是變態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「變態」這詞我可不能當作沒聽到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就是這樣 雖然不敢跟別人說 但心裡卻想「這種程度是OK的」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想 就像對著喜歡的女孩子的豎笛接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷掉她自行車的坐鞍之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才這樣做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 大小姐學校的真實狀況 都是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來你跟御坂同屋 你們同一個年級嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你叫她做「姐姐大人」 還以為你肯定是她學妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡 我的確就是姐姐大人的晚輩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年級也比她低
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是讓她的前任室友退出 然後自己補上罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 是在合法範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人的敵人也是很多的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說這是有力量的人的孽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不覺得連睡同一房間的人都是叛徒 這樣會太痛苦了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 我能認為你就是平常就跟姐姐大人頻繁起爭執的男士麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯了的話 也沒啥關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只是想稍微看看作為姐姐大人心靈支柱的男士的樣子罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈支柱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這腳步聲...糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍監好像來巡房了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 被她知道常盤臺女生宿舍有男人在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.74,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,440)}<Teleport>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就用空間移動 送你到外面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我的力量對你不管用？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:19.83,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(550,440)}<Imagine Breaker>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 那個 肯定是因為我的右手...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 請你先躲到床底下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這縫隙 太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井 到晚餐時間了 快到食堂集合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？御坂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人還在補習 估計是拖堂了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有收到這個報告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她過了門限還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室友將負上連帶責任 扣一分 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 這是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鏈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.07,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,440)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「妹妹」是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.29,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『由量產異能者「妹妹」的運用使「一方通行」向絕對能力的進化法』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.29,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\pos(204,30)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.29,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\pos(398,30)}<Accelerator Level 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.29,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\pos(540,30)}<Level 6>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.02,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(414,440)}<Level 6>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.06,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304,440)}<Tree Diagram>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用樹形圖設計者預測演算過後的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判斷得出 能到達絕對能力者 Level 6的人只有一名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過準備好特定的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照劇本來進行戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由實戰促進其成長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然看不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有吹風 螺旋槳竟然在轉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風力發電 是通過螺旋槳轉動而發電
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來 通過給予電力 螺旋槳就會轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的身體 應該總是會發出電磁波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 跟著這個來追的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫在報告上面的 極具衝擊性的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:29.65,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(439,440)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這個背負著妹妹殘酷的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就被壓垮的御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.73,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(474,440)}<Level 6>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 絕對能力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學與魔術交錯之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事就開始了


